WEBVTT

00:00:10.115 --> 00:00:12.117
Song Hui-na's contract ends
in three months.

00:00:12.200 --> 00:00:14.452
Team 1, get in touch and check with her.

00:00:14.953 --> 00:00:17.163
Any ideas for the empty Tuesday slot?

00:00:17.247 --> 00:00:21.000
We're targeting a genre that clearly
differentiates us from our competitors.

00:00:21.084 --> 00:00:24.462
For now, the most likely candidates
are Hwany and Jingom.

00:00:24.546 --> 00:00:26.798
Oh, and how's Friday coming along?

00:00:26.881 --> 00:00:30.218
Another company ran a promotion last week.
It didn't hurt us, did it?

00:00:30.301 --> 00:00:31.970
What is she up to?

00:00:32.053 --> 00:00:34.597
Yun Song suddenly went on hiatus, so…

00:00:34.681 --> 00:00:38.601
If you can't control your authors,
you should have a contingency plan!

00:00:38.685 --> 00:00:40.687
Stay sharp, or we could fall behind fast!

00:00:40.770 --> 00:00:44.190
This goes for all of you, okay?
Keep that in mind.

00:00:51.948 --> 00:00:54.033
-Thank you.
-Sure.

00:01:05.170 --> 00:01:07.172
It's finally here.

00:01:09.841 --> 00:01:11.426
-You have to go with me.
-Okay.

00:01:11.509 --> 00:01:12.760
Look, isn't it pretty?

00:01:13.261 --> 00:01:15.513
I can't wait to see it!

00:01:20.101 --> 00:01:21.436
At first, it was just

00:01:23.354 --> 00:01:25.023
a string of coincidences.

00:01:28.610 --> 00:01:31.321
I ran into her when I least expected it.

00:01:33.698 --> 00:01:34.699
Mere coincidence.

00:01:44.500 --> 00:01:46.836
Next up, Seo Mi-rae. Pick your gift.

00:01:47.337 --> 00:01:49.214
Pick a cute one!

00:01:49.297 --> 00:01:50.131
What is it?

00:01:52.383 --> 00:01:53.218
No way!

00:01:56.262 --> 00:01:58.264
-Thank you.
-It looks like you!

00:01:58.348 --> 00:02:00.516
So adorable. It looks just like you!

00:02:01.267 --> 00:02:03.645
Of all the gifts there, you picked mine.

00:02:05.230 --> 00:02:06.064
A coincidence.

00:02:14.197 --> 00:02:16.157
Every day, we got on the same elevator.

00:02:18.868 --> 00:02:19.702
A coincidence.

00:02:46.104 --> 00:02:46.938
I realized then…

00:02:49.399 --> 00:02:52.068
that I was waiting
for another coincidence.

00:02:55.738 --> 00:02:56.739
That won't work.

00:02:59.409 --> 00:03:00.243
Okay.

00:03:03.538 --> 00:03:07.125
Some days, I got a little greedy.

00:03:09.460 --> 00:03:10.837
Cliché.

00:03:12.213 --> 00:03:14.465
Not a cliché, but a classic.

00:03:23.182 --> 00:03:24.475
One iced Americano, please.

00:03:24.559 --> 00:03:26.269
And an iced latte with that.

00:03:32.317 --> 00:03:33.901
-Here to buy coffee?
-Yes.

00:03:33.985 --> 00:03:35.611
Iced latte, please.

00:03:35.695 --> 00:03:37.238
That will be 4,500 won.

00:03:40.033 --> 00:03:41.451
Thank you.

00:03:44.370 --> 00:03:48.082
Some days, I tried to act
like I didn't care and give up.

00:03:48.166 --> 00:03:50.126
Ta-da! It's this, right?

00:04:00.178 --> 00:04:01.012
There we go.

00:04:04.182 --> 00:04:06.476
But whenever I did, you would…

00:04:21.282 --> 00:04:22.700
You actually made it?

00:04:26.788 --> 00:04:28.539
…keep stepping into my side.

00:04:53.523 --> 00:04:58.027
EPISODE 7
THE ALGORITHM OF FEELINGS

00:05:01.155 --> 00:05:02.407
So warm.

00:05:19.465 --> 00:05:20.675
What are you doing here?

00:05:25.847 --> 00:05:26.722
Hello?

00:05:27.849 --> 00:05:28.724
Hello?

00:05:41.237 --> 00:05:42.238
Mr. Park…

00:05:46.742 --> 00:05:47.618
Why are you here?

00:05:48.202 --> 00:05:49.036
Oh, I…

00:05:49.829 --> 00:05:50.663
I just…

00:05:54.709 --> 00:05:58.379
I was just getting some fresh air.
I was just about to head inside.

00:06:00.465 --> 00:06:01.299
Then let's go.

00:06:01.382 --> 00:06:04.135
No, I'm good. I can go by myself.

00:06:04.802 --> 00:06:05.720
You're tipsy.

00:06:06.554 --> 00:06:08.806
I'm really fine though…

00:06:29.827 --> 00:06:31.204
Back there,

00:06:31.704 --> 00:06:34.540
you said, "You actually made it."

00:06:37.043 --> 00:06:38.294
What did you mean by that?

00:06:39.545 --> 00:06:42.131
It was probably the alcohol. I'm sorry.

00:06:42.215 --> 00:06:44.008
Did you mistake me for someone else?

00:06:44.091 --> 00:06:47.178
No. It's not like that.

00:06:48.679 --> 00:06:53.100
But weren't you drinking with the others?

00:06:53.601 --> 00:06:54.852
Why did you come out here?

00:06:54.936 --> 00:06:55.853
I just thought

00:06:57.146 --> 00:06:58.773
I might get some fresh air too.

00:07:05.238 --> 00:07:06.989
Is your relationship going well?

00:07:12.620 --> 00:07:13.454
Yes.

00:07:16.499 --> 00:07:17.667
Glad to hear it.

00:07:37.812 --> 00:07:39.313
This is my room.

00:07:39.897 --> 00:07:40.731
Okay.

00:07:42.316 --> 00:07:43.276
Good night.

00:07:44.527 --> 00:07:45.444
Good night.

00:08:16.726 --> 00:08:19.270
Kyeong-nam, where are you?
Why aren't you coming back?

00:08:19.353 --> 00:08:22.023
Dong-min's totally hammered right now.

00:08:22.106 --> 00:08:23.691
It's hilarious!

00:08:23.774 --> 00:08:25.526
Hye-bin's more drunk than I am.

00:08:25.610 --> 00:08:28.863
Did you go back to your room?
You're coming back, right?

00:08:33.993 --> 00:08:37.955
I'm tired, so I'm going to sleep now.
Have fun, everyone.

00:09:04.357 --> 00:09:07.151
Did Mi-rae pass out with Yun Song
after taking her back?

00:09:10.321 --> 00:09:13.032
Yeah. I guess I was really tired.

00:09:13.115 --> 00:09:14.325
Have fun, guys.

00:09:17.119 --> 00:09:18.663
She's always lying.

00:09:19.622 --> 00:09:21.749
Ms. Yun, I just got us a taxi.

00:09:21.832 --> 00:09:24.418
Time for you to go to your room
and go to bed. Okay?

00:09:24.502 --> 00:09:26.629
-Give me your arm.
-Let me go!

00:09:27.546 --> 00:09:31.884
Hey, why won't you ever date anyone?

00:09:31.967 --> 00:09:35.805
You had a boyfriend
back when you used to work with me.

00:09:35.888 --> 00:09:38.474
You haven't met anyone
since you broke up with him, huh?

00:09:40.393 --> 00:09:42.728
Why are you bringing that up now?

00:09:42.812 --> 00:09:46.732
Besides, how am I supposed to date anyone
when you're always giving me a hard time?

00:09:46.816 --> 00:09:52.363
If no one likes you, you should at least
have a crush on someone.

00:09:52.446 --> 00:09:55.658
I'll handle that myself, okay?
The taxi's here. Let's go.

00:09:55.741 --> 00:09:57.993
I'm going!

00:09:58.077 --> 00:10:00.746
I have two cats at home.
They're super adorable.

00:10:00.830 --> 00:10:03.457
I think I'll step outside for a bit.

00:10:03.541 --> 00:10:04.375
Huh?

00:10:05.710 --> 00:10:06.836
Don't take too long.

00:10:15.511 --> 00:10:19.265
The person you are calling
is not available. Please leave a message…

00:10:51.088 --> 00:10:52.715
CHOI DONG-MIN

00:10:57.887 --> 00:10:58.721
Hello?

00:10:58.804 --> 00:11:02.391
Kyeong-nam. Where are you, man?
Hwany is looking for you.

00:11:03.726 --> 00:11:04.852
I stepped outside and…

00:11:04.935 --> 00:11:05.936
Come back already.

00:11:06.020 --> 00:11:08.022
Come on, man. Where are you?

00:11:08.105 --> 00:11:09.523
Hey, where's Mi-rae?

00:11:09.607 --> 00:11:10.441
Huh?

00:11:11.358 --> 00:11:13.694
Mi-rae, where are you?

00:11:13.778 --> 00:11:15.780
Ms. Seo's not with you?

00:11:15.863 --> 00:11:20.034
She told Hye-bin that she left the hotel,
but she didn't come here.

00:11:20.117 --> 00:11:21.786
Where's she gone this time?

00:11:22.745 --> 00:11:23.913
Hurry back!

00:11:54.819 --> 00:11:56.862
Why do I keep getting my hopes up?

00:12:06.664 --> 00:12:09.583
I shouldn't be happy
that she doesn't have a boyfriend.

00:12:10.709 --> 00:12:12.294
Is your relationship going well?

00:12:16.048 --> 00:12:16.882
Yes.

00:12:18.008 --> 00:12:20.344
She's lying to me
about having a boyfriend.

00:12:21.971 --> 00:12:23.097
Glad to hear it.

00:12:24.348 --> 00:12:26.016
Think about what that means.

00:12:39.363 --> 00:12:41.198
It's about time I accepted it.

00:12:54.545 --> 00:12:55.880
Be right there.

00:12:59.341 --> 00:13:00.175
Ms. Yun.

00:13:01.218 --> 00:13:02.136
Let's go.

00:13:03.387 --> 00:13:04.221
What?

00:13:04.305 --> 00:13:05.306
Ms. Yun!

00:13:05.389 --> 00:13:08.434
We didn't even have breakfast.
Why are you in such a hurry?

00:13:08.517 --> 00:13:10.895
Breakfast? Who needs breakfast?

00:13:13.731 --> 00:13:15.649
You did drink too much last night--

00:13:15.733 --> 00:13:17.359
Stop talking about last night!

00:13:19.528 --> 00:13:22.114
What? Did something happen last night?

00:13:23.991 --> 00:13:26.076
I knew it. It was just a dream, wasn't it?

00:13:27.369 --> 00:13:31.123
You received an award yesterday,
and then we went for a drink…

00:13:31.999 --> 00:13:34.335
Oh, then you told Hwany--

00:13:34.418 --> 00:13:35.252
Stop!

00:13:37.421 --> 00:13:39.632
What am I going to do now? Keep up.

00:13:41.258 --> 00:13:42.468
Oh, right.

00:13:42.551 --> 00:13:45.304
Did you remember
to call your boyfriend back?

00:13:45.387 --> 00:13:46.597
What?

00:13:46.680 --> 00:13:50.309
I didn't believe you at first,
but he was gentle, with a great voice.

00:13:51.602 --> 00:13:52.728
How did you know about…

00:13:53.312 --> 00:13:57.066
While you were passed out last night,
I answered a call from your boyfriend.

00:13:57.149 --> 00:13:58.150
Hey!

00:13:58.817 --> 00:14:01.153
-Why the hell would you do that?
-What?

00:14:02.237 --> 00:14:05.366
The phone kept ringing, so I figured
someone must be very worried--

00:14:05.449 --> 00:14:07.785
You're really annoying!

00:14:09.078 --> 00:14:10.371
Ms. Yun!

00:14:11.622 --> 00:14:13.290
What's her problem?

00:14:24.259 --> 00:14:25.302
Kyeong-nam!

00:14:26.220 --> 00:14:29.431
Man, I'm dying here.
Let's go and get some gukbap.

00:14:29.932 --> 00:14:31.433
-And the others?
-Getting coffee.

00:14:33.102 --> 00:14:34.353
Here. Coffee!

00:14:35.646 --> 00:14:36.772
Mr. Park, your coffee.

00:14:36.855 --> 00:14:37.982
Thank you.

00:14:38.065 --> 00:14:39.274
Hot coffee for me.

00:14:40.901 --> 00:14:41.902
Where's Mi-rae?

00:14:43.904 --> 00:14:45.656
She and Ms. Yun left early.

00:14:57.793 --> 00:14:58.919
Hangover cure, everyone?

00:14:59.003 --> 00:15:00.254
-Sounds good.
-Let's go.

00:15:00.337 --> 00:15:01.171
Yeah.

00:15:01.255 --> 00:15:05.009
Hey, why did you leave me so early
last night?

00:15:05.092 --> 00:15:06.510
God, you reek of alcohol.

00:15:07.011 --> 00:15:08.345
Don't be like that, partner.

00:15:08.429 --> 00:15:09.847
Get away from me.

00:15:09.930 --> 00:15:11.765
Kyeong-nam, why didn't you come back?

00:15:11.849 --> 00:15:13.183
Don't be such a stranger!

00:15:23.444 --> 00:15:26.613
Sure enough, there's no place like home.

00:15:39.376 --> 00:15:40.419
DONG-MIN SENT 10 PHOTOS

00:15:45.466 --> 00:15:47.801
Looks like they had fun.

00:16:07.696 --> 00:16:09.865
-Hello?
-Did you get home safely yesterday?

00:16:12.367 --> 00:16:13.202
I did.

00:16:14.078 --> 00:16:16.497
I felt bad about
not being able to go yesterday.

00:16:18.123 --> 00:16:19.374
It's okay.

00:16:19.458 --> 00:16:22.336
I was surprised to get a call from you.

00:16:22.419 --> 00:16:25.047
I thought if I saw your face,
it'd be hard for me to leave.

00:16:25.130 --> 00:16:26.840
But I guess you weren't that sad.

00:16:27.800 --> 00:16:30.219
What do you mean? Are you going somewhere?

00:16:30.302 --> 00:16:31.553
Let's talk in person.

00:16:32.429 --> 00:16:33.347
Right now?

00:16:35.349 --> 00:16:36.433
I'll be waiting.

00:16:55.452 --> 00:16:57.496
What was that? What's going on?

00:16:57.579 --> 00:16:58.831
You're here early.

00:16:59.414 --> 00:17:00.624
Would you like a drink?

00:17:02.167 --> 00:17:03.001
No.

00:17:03.085 --> 00:17:04.419
Okay, then.

00:17:09.925 --> 00:17:11.468
So where are you going?

00:17:12.886 --> 00:17:14.763
I've been here way too long.

00:17:14.847 --> 00:17:18.475
That wasn't the plan,
but then I met a certain someone here.

00:17:19.726 --> 00:17:21.478
It's time for me to move on.

00:17:23.897 --> 00:17:25.315
Where will you be going?

00:17:25.399 --> 00:17:29.027
Nothing's decided yet.
I'll see where the road takes me.

00:17:31.071 --> 00:17:33.323
Then will you be going by yourself?

00:17:38.078 --> 00:17:39.413
Will you go with me?

00:17:42.082 --> 00:17:45.752
We can travel together,
go sightseeing, and try delicious food.

00:17:47.754 --> 00:17:50.132
I suppose you could chalk it up
to my profession,

00:17:50.757 --> 00:17:53.760
but the moment I heard those words,
I realized.

00:17:54.803 --> 00:17:56.096
I want to go with you.

00:17:59.224 --> 00:18:01.435
My journey with Gu Yeong-il

00:18:03.270 --> 00:18:06.106
was only just beginning.

00:18:28.921 --> 00:18:30.547
It'll be ready in a bit.

00:18:30.631 --> 00:18:32.007
-It looks good.
-Let's eat.

00:18:33.008 --> 00:18:34.593
Like this. Hang on.

00:18:37.804 --> 00:18:38.639
How is it?

00:18:47.356 --> 00:18:48.440
Nice and cool, huh?

00:19:45.330 --> 00:19:47.499
Come with me.

00:19:51.712 --> 00:19:52.838
What are you doing here?

00:20:03.181 --> 00:20:04.224
Why are you here?

00:20:05.642 --> 00:20:07.561
Why does that keep happening?

00:20:10.063 --> 00:20:10.897
Seo Mi-rae.

00:20:11.857 --> 00:20:12.858
Ms. Seo.

00:20:14.443 --> 00:20:15.861
Right now…

00:20:16.445 --> 00:20:17.279
What is it?

00:20:17.362 --> 00:20:18.655
Why do you do that?

00:20:19.364 --> 00:20:20.824
…who am I with?

00:20:35.213 --> 00:20:36.048
What was that?

00:20:36.548 --> 00:20:38.633
Why can't I separate the two?

00:20:39.676 --> 00:20:41.261
This isn't how it's supposed to be.

00:20:46.516 --> 00:20:50.020
I just got home. See you all tomorrow.

00:21:16.713 --> 00:21:17.547
Hello.

00:21:17.631 --> 00:21:18.465
Hi.

00:21:25.764 --> 00:21:29.851
Our company really made waves this time.
Am I right?

00:21:30.852 --> 00:21:34.773
But compared to the major platforms,
we still have a long way to go.

00:21:34.856 --> 00:21:36.191
You know that, right?

00:21:36.274 --> 00:21:39.027
Let's stay focused
on both artistic quality and public appeal

00:21:39.111 --> 00:21:42.114
and work toward winning
another award next year. Okay?

00:21:42.656 --> 00:21:45.325
On that note,
I'd like to add that yesterday…

00:21:45.409 --> 00:21:48.370
He might be avoiding me. Fair enough.

00:21:48.870 --> 00:21:51.623
-Aren't we all blessed with work!
-I know, right?

00:21:51.706 --> 00:21:54.793
I feel bad for Mr. Park.
You've already got so much on your plate.

00:21:54.876 --> 00:21:55.710
I know.

00:21:55.794 --> 00:21:58.338
It's still a good thing.
I'll take things one at a time.

00:21:58.422 --> 00:22:01.466
Anyway, are you doing okay?
That event looks like a lot of work.

00:22:01.550 --> 00:22:04.386
It is. That's why you should help me out.

00:22:05.095 --> 00:22:06.054
I'd be happy to.

00:22:07.305 --> 00:22:11.226
We're not even on the same team,
so it's totally understandable.

00:22:11.309 --> 00:22:13.103
He's Park Kyeong-nam, after all.

00:22:13.186 --> 00:22:14.020
Oh, right.

00:22:19.234 --> 00:22:21.069
Let's pick this up when we get there.

00:22:21.153 --> 00:22:22.154
Okay.

00:22:22.237 --> 00:22:23.989
I'm going to have some makgeolli.

00:22:24.072 --> 00:22:25.157
You know I don't drink.

00:22:25.240 --> 00:22:27.409
-Come on. That's not fair.
-Come on.

00:22:27.492 --> 00:22:29.327
-Yeah, drink with us.
-Damn it!

00:22:29.411 --> 00:22:30.412
You're no fun.

00:22:32.539 --> 00:22:33.623
Wait a minute.

00:22:34.458 --> 00:22:36.126
Why am I avoiding him?

00:22:50.390 --> 00:22:53.477
Can't we just have dinner tomorrow?
It's cold today.

00:22:54.728 --> 00:22:58.398
I'll be there within 30 minutes.
Wait there. I think I took the wrong turn.

00:22:58.482 --> 00:23:01.485
Hey, come on… Let me…

00:23:02.068 --> 00:23:03.278
Seriously?

00:23:03.361 --> 00:23:05.447
Hey, just let me in!

00:23:08.700 --> 00:23:10.452
I'll wait for you at the café.

00:23:13.830 --> 00:23:15.123
Hello, Ms. Seo.

00:23:15.207 --> 00:23:17.876
Hello. What brings you here?

00:23:17.959 --> 00:23:20.128
I'm here for a meeting with Kyeong-nam.

00:23:23.507 --> 00:23:25.258
Your latte is ready.

00:23:26.343 --> 00:23:27.427
Damn it.

00:23:29.846 --> 00:23:32.516
Yes. It's just like Park Kyeong-nam said.

00:23:32.599 --> 00:23:35.435
I'm not the one who got rejected.
I don't have to keep this up.

00:23:44.778 --> 00:23:46.112
Be confident.

00:23:47.781 --> 00:23:49.199
Stand tall.

00:23:51.660 --> 00:23:52.827
And smile.

00:23:55.205 --> 00:23:57.499
What? Too pretty to handle?

00:24:10.262 --> 00:24:12.681
Are you okay? That was really loud.

00:24:14.641 --> 00:24:15.976
I'm totally fine.

00:24:16.560 --> 00:24:18.311
It was just loud, that's all.

00:24:22.482 --> 00:24:25.986
Code red. Where are you?
I'm gonna wait outside.

00:24:27.821 --> 00:24:30.657
How come?
I'll be at least another 20 minutes.

00:24:30.740 --> 00:24:33.410
Hey, it's freezing outside.
Just stay there.

00:24:33.493 --> 00:24:34.828
I'll be there soon.

00:24:40.500 --> 00:24:41.459
Are you leaving?

00:24:42.168 --> 00:24:44.337
Oh, I just need to use the restroom.

00:24:48.633 --> 00:24:49.926
I'm worried about her.

00:24:56.308 --> 00:24:57.350
What is this?

00:24:58.059 --> 00:24:59.477
When did this show up?

00:25:03.315 --> 00:25:04.899
What am I gonna do?

00:25:12.073 --> 00:25:13.074
Goodbye.

00:25:14.159 --> 00:25:15.660
Put some ointment on that, okay?

00:25:20.290 --> 00:25:21.625
She's so scatterbrained.

00:25:21.708 --> 00:25:23.877
She's going to hit her head again soon.

00:25:23.960 --> 00:25:25.211
Where were we?

00:25:28.131 --> 00:25:29.132
Hold on a second.

00:25:43.063 --> 00:25:43.897
Look alike much?

00:25:51.905 --> 00:25:53.448
I'm so sorry.

00:25:53.531 --> 00:25:57.077
I think I've turned my blinker on
a hundred times on my way here.

00:25:57.994 --> 00:25:58.828
Hey!

00:25:58.912 --> 00:26:00.038
What happened there?

00:26:00.705 --> 00:26:01.956
Did you get into a fight?

00:26:02.040 --> 00:26:03.208
No.

00:26:03.708 --> 00:26:06.586
-Hey, let's just get out of here. Hurry!
-Okay.

00:26:07.587 --> 00:26:10.465
Goddamn it,
that was freaking embarrassing!

00:26:10.548 --> 00:26:12.550
Hey, come on. Let's go.

00:26:12.634 --> 00:26:13.468
Okay.

00:26:13.551 --> 00:26:14.636
-Go!
-Okay.

00:26:20.642 --> 00:26:21.476
Here.

00:26:22.519 --> 00:26:23.353
Thanks.

00:26:27.357 --> 00:26:29.359
Hey, just laugh out loud.

00:26:33.780 --> 00:26:34.948
Hold up.

00:26:35.031 --> 00:26:37.575
You got hit pretty hard.
Just how were you walking?

00:26:37.659 --> 00:26:41.037
Hey. If you hadn't brought your car
and ended up being late…

00:26:41.955 --> 00:26:42.789
Forget it.

00:26:43.498 --> 00:26:47.419
I was only trying to let you ride along
in comfort on this cold day.

00:26:49.087 --> 00:26:51.423
How are you even free today?
No more blind dates?

00:26:51.506 --> 00:26:52.340
Huh?

00:26:55.260 --> 00:26:57.178
I'm just taking a break.

00:26:59.013 --> 00:27:00.014
How come?

00:27:00.557 --> 00:27:02.976
I don't know.
I just think it's a waste of time.

00:27:05.437 --> 00:27:06.896
Someone's a copycat.

00:27:08.690 --> 00:27:11.526
I mean, I get dolled up
early in the morning

00:27:11.609 --> 00:27:14.988
just to see a guy I don't even like,
acting all cute and polite.

00:27:15.071 --> 00:27:17.949
Then I get home, wash off my makeup,
and feel so pathetic.

00:27:18.032 --> 00:27:22.787
"Am I wasting my peak years?"
That's how it makes me feel.

00:27:22.871 --> 00:27:25.540
Could there be something more fun
than dating in the world,

00:27:25.623 --> 00:27:27.625
and I'm the only one
who doesn't know about it?

00:27:27.709 --> 00:27:30.462
Hey, starting now,
you should look into that.

00:27:31.963 --> 00:27:35.592
Nope. I don't think
there's anything more fun than dating.

00:27:36.801 --> 00:27:39.387
It's just that it's so damn hard
to find a guy I like!

00:27:41.264 --> 00:27:43.600
Are you talking to yourself?
Why ask if you had an answer?

00:27:44.100 --> 00:27:46.936
Anyway, think about
how you're going to deal with that.

00:27:47.020 --> 00:27:48.438
You can't go to work like that.

00:27:58.198 --> 00:28:01.618
Perfect. It's just perfect.
You can't tell at all.

00:28:01.701 --> 00:28:02.535
Really?

00:28:06.414 --> 00:28:09.083
Seriously? I think it's pretty obvious.

00:28:09.876 --> 00:28:11.127
Should I just cut my bangs?

00:28:12.378 --> 00:28:15.423
Don't you know that 97% of women
who get bangs regret it right away?

00:28:16.007 --> 00:28:19.886
As soon as you get them, it becomes
your goal to grow your hair out again.

00:28:19.969 --> 00:28:21.513
You'll thank me later.

00:28:28.353 --> 00:28:31.439
You got a haircut? It looks good on you.

00:28:31.523 --> 00:28:33.274
-Very nice.
-Thank you.

00:28:33.358 --> 00:28:34.609
It suits you well.

00:28:34.692 --> 00:28:36.444
-Oh my God!
-Wow.

00:28:39.072 --> 00:28:39.906
What's going on?

00:28:40.406 --> 00:28:41.908
Oh, is it a wig?

00:28:42.742 --> 00:28:43.827
Does it show?

00:28:43.910 --> 00:28:45.286
A little from up close.

00:28:46.538 --> 00:28:48.748
What happened?
Are you going for a new look?

00:28:49.707 --> 00:28:50.542
Huh?

00:28:51.918 --> 00:28:53.920
No, it's not like that.

00:28:54.003 --> 00:28:57.006
I just felt
like changing things up a little.

00:29:11.104 --> 00:29:12.438
Hello.

00:29:18.862 --> 00:29:19.946
What do we have here?

00:29:21.072 --> 00:29:22.490
A sudden change in hairstyle?

00:29:32.375 --> 00:29:34.377
God, so embarrassing.

00:29:37.088 --> 00:29:38.006
You crazy bitch…

00:29:38.089 --> 00:29:41.259
I honestly wasn't going to bring this up.

00:29:42.176 --> 00:29:43.970
-What?
-Are you not over me yet?

00:29:44.053 --> 00:29:45.597
You crazy bitch!

00:29:48.558 --> 00:29:49.392
Ms. Yun.

00:29:49.475 --> 00:29:51.352
-Are you okay?
-What do you mean?

00:29:51.436 --> 00:29:55.648
You've been having these random outbursts
for the last few days,

00:29:55.732 --> 00:29:57.233
which is a little strange.

00:29:57.317 --> 00:29:58.151
Huh?

00:29:58.234 --> 00:30:00.737
You were the one who secretly left snacks
in front of my room.

00:30:00.820 --> 00:30:02.739
Hold it right there. That was…

00:30:02.822 --> 00:30:03.740
-Those were…
-What?

00:30:04.324 --> 00:30:05.742
Those were meant for So-yeong!

00:30:11.372 --> 00:30:13.833
So-yeong, just go. Get out.

00:30:13.917 --> 00:30:15.668
I'm really struggling right now. Go.

00:30:15.752 --> 00:30:17.086
Okay.

00:30:22.592 --> 00:30:24.510
Are you kidding me?

00:30:29.933 --> 00:30:32.185
I'll give you just ten more minutes.

00:30:45.949 --> 00:30:46.908
What?

00:30:54.791 --> 00:30:56.042
God, it's cold.

00:30:58.628 --> 00:31:01.130
Come on. Don't do this to me!

00:31:04.926 --> 00:31:06.094
Just 30 more minutes.

00:31:06.886 --> 00:31:08.096
Seriously?

00:31:08.638 --> 00:31:10.431
It's always 30 minutes with her.

00:31:18.356 --> 00:31:19.190
Cold!

00:31:27.907 --> 00:31:28.741
Oh God…

00:31:41.963 --> 00:31:43.381
I was cold too.

00:31:56.144 --> 00:31:57.854
This was the only heater we had.

00:32:01.065 --> 00:32:02.400
Oh, but…

00:32:04.902 --> 00:32:07.196
You said you were cold too.

00:32:07.697 --> 00:32:08.906
Let's share it.

00:32:21.544 --> 00:32:23.296
How's that bump from yesterday?

00:32:24.130 --> 00:32:27.133
Oh, it's gone down a lot.

00:32:30.720 --> 00:32:31.637
That's a relief.

00:32:41.230 --> 00:32:44.901
Dong-min said you guys came back to Seoul
later than usual on Sunday.

00:32:44.984 --> 00:32:46.819
I guess you had a lot of fun.

00:32:48.571 --> 00:32:49.989
Yes, well,

00:32:50.073 --> 00:32:52.492
we saw the ocean and had some good food.

00:32:54.994 --> 00:32:55.828
We just…

00:32:56.621 --> 00:32:57.538
Yeah.

00:32:58.623 --> 00:33:01.709
I saw the pictures,
and I was really jealous.

00:33:01.793 --> 00:33:06.297
Ms. Yun wanted to come back early,
so I had to eat ramyeon at the airport.

00:33:08.925 --> 00:33:10.259
Then did you

00:33:11.552 --> 00:33:12.887
want to stay longer?

00:33:23.856 --> 00:33:24.690
Well…

00:33:25.399 --> 00:33:28.778
Yes, I wanted to stay
and have good food as well.

00:33:30.071 --> 00:33:33.074
Next time,
I plan on staying a little longer.

00:33:36.869 --> 00:33:37.870
I see.

00:33:47.880 --> 00:33:48.714
UPLOAD COMPLETE

00:34:23.958 --> 00:34:25.835
I'll see you tomorrow.

00:34:26.586 --> 00:34:27.420
Right.

00:35:04.624 --> 00:35:07.877
I WANTED TO TELL YOU THAT I LIKE YOU

00:36:03.891 --> 00:36:06.894
I wanted to tell you that I like you.

00:36:18.114 --> 00:36:19.615
Did you get my letter?

00:36:21.242 --> 00:36:23.494
This is kind of embarrassing.

00:36:23.577 --> 00:36:24.495
What's this?

00:36:24.578 --> 00:36:25.413
To be honest,

00:36:26.789 --> 00:36:28.291
I was a little mad at you.

00:36:29.000 --> 00:36:32.044
For not even answering me
when I asked you to come with me.

00:36:33.296 --> 00:36:36.132
So I was just going to get over you, but

00:36:37.341 --> 00:36:38.718
it's harder than I thought.

00:36:40.970 --> 00:36:42.054
I miss you.

00:37:24.972 --> 00:37:26.766
1: PLANC
2: THE MAN TO KNOW

00:37:30.603 --> 00:37:32.938
TMTK was number one forever until today.

00:37:33.022 --> 00:37:35.524
-Once you slip, it's all downhill.
-Deepest condolences.

00:37:35.608 --> 00:37:38.110
-It lasted longer than expected.
-Hwany sure is no joke.

00:37:38.194 --> 00:37:40.279
Isn't this the first time
she got dethroned?

00:37:41.572 --> 00:37:44.158
Winning an award sure does help a lot,
doesn't it?

00:37:44.241 --> 00:37:45.493
Don't get excited just yet.

00:37:45.576 --> 00:37:48.079
Would it kill you to play along for once?

00:37:48.162 --> 00:37:50.247
You saw what happened to me in Busan.

00:37:51.040 --> 00:37:53.209
What are you doing tomorrow?
Let's get a drink.

00:37:53.292 --> 00:37:54.210
Aren't you working?

00:37:54.293 --> 00:37:57.922
This calls for a proper celebration.
I might lose my spot next week, after all.

00:37:59.340 --> 00:38:00.841
Okay. I'll get back to you.

00:38:15.022 --> 00:38:17.483
-Yeah. I had absolutely no idea.
-I know.

00:38:18.484 --> 00:38:19.568
Hey!

00:38:19.652 --> 00:38:21.320
-Hi, Mi-rae.
-Hi.

00:38:29.286 --> 00:38:30.538
Are you okay?

00:38:32.123 --> 00:38:33.624
Yup, I'm okay.

00:38:34.125 --> 00:38:37.294
It happens all the time.
Don't worry about it too much.

00:38:37.378 --> 00:38:38.212
Sure.

00:38:38.295 --> 00:38:40.464
It can make it back to the top!

00:38:40.548 --> 00:38:41.549
Definitely.

00:38:41.632 --> 00:38:44.885
Sure, they are going to keep
trading places,

00:38:44.969 --> 00:38:48.305
but all you need is for the author
to keep her head. Right?

00:38:58.232 --> 00:38:59.066
Oh man.

00:39:02.695 --> 00:39:06.407
Cheer up, it's okay. These things happen.

00:39:06.490 --> 00:39:10.286
PlanC won a big award,
and it got a lot of press, after all.

00:39:14.373 --> 00:39:15.291
Mr. Hwang.

00:39:15.374 --> 00:39:17.084
So what's the game plan now?

00:39:18.294 --> 00:39:20.671
-What?
-You do have a plan, don't you?

00:39:22.089 --> 00:39:24.675
Oh, right. Well, I…

00:39:24.758 --> 00:39:28.637
I'll put in the work with Ms. Yun
to give it our best shot.

00:39:29.722 --> 00:39:30.723
Hey, Seo Mi-rae.

00:39:32.057 --> 00:39:35.352
Do you have any idea how much
the coin sales for TMTK have fallen?

00:39:36.145 --> 00:39:37.146
What?

00:39:38.314 --> 00:39:40.441
Yun Song's contract is almost up.

00:39:40.524 --> 00:39:43.819
At this rate, we'll never renew
the contract on good terms.

00:39:43.903 --> 00:39:46.489
Her next season
would have to be the final one.

00:39:47.281 --> 00:39:50.618
You have other authors to manage.
Stop letting her drag you around.

00:39:50.701 --> 00:39:52.119
It's exhausting.

00:39:52.203 --> 00:39:55.539
I'll talk to her and see what I can do.

00:39:56.123 --> 00:39:59.251
Okay. So how?
How will you talk to her about it?

00:40:00.002 --> 00:40:00.836
Excuse me?

00:40:03.464 --> 00:40:04.673
So you're clueless.

00:40:06.175 --> 00:40:09.094
Hey, you're not blameless here.
You know that?

00:40:09.178 --> 00:40:13.098
If the producer gives it everything,
the title doesn't sink so easily.

00:40:13.182 --> 00:40:15.434
But look at what you've done!

00:40:15.518 --> 00:40:17.186
She's our most expensive author,

00:40:17.269 --> 00:40:19.772
and look what happened
in just a few months.

00:40:19.855 --> 00:40:21.106
I'm sorry, sir.

00:40:24.944 --> 00:40:25.861
Hello?

00:40:33.827 --> 00:40:34.912
I'm not sure.

00:40:34.995 --> 00:40:37.706
She hasn't been lashing out as usual,
and she's being quiet.

00:40:41.377 --> 00:40:43.128
I'll come over tomorrow.

00:40:43.837 --> 00:40:44.922
I said go.

00:40:45.923 --> 00:40:47.841
Your words of comfort
won't change a thing.

00:40:48.717 --> 00:40:50.469
Just throw a fit instead.

00:40:51.637 --> 00:40:54.181
I knew this day would come eventually.

00:40:55.224 --> 00:40:56.809
It's a downward spiral.

00:40:57.476 --> 00:40:58.978
That's all there is to it.

00:41:01.522 --> 00:41:02.648
Ms. Yun.

00:41:04.900 --> 00:41:06.443
I told you, didn't I?

00:41:07.486 --> 00:41:10.990
I only blew up because of Choi Si-woo.
I don't have what it takes.

00:41:13.409 --> 00:41:15.327
It's time for me to put it all down.

00:41:16.370 --> 00:41:20.040
Sell my car, sell my home,

00:41:20.833 --> 00:41:22.918
and sell… the building.

00:41:23.836 --> 00:41:26.672
What's this about selling stuff?

00:41:26.755 --> 00:41:27.590
Ms. Yun.

00:41:27.673 --> 00:41:30.718
I'm not going to give up
on TMTK like this.

00:41:30.801 --> 00:41:34.013
It's true that I was distracted
by some personal stuff,

00:41:34.096 --> 00:41:37.808
and I'm sorry I couldn't give it
everything I've got.

00:41:37.891 --> 00:41:39.184
What personal stuff?

00:41:40.644 --> 00:41:41.937
You slacked off, didn't you?

00:41:42.021 --> 00:41:44.523
No, it's not like that. I…

00:41:45.274 --> 00:41:48.611
Anyway, I'm going to go all-in
from now on.

00:41:48.694 --> 00:41:51.989
So I need you to get a grip too. Okay?

00:41:52.072 --> 00:41:56.744
I'll do whatever it takes
to get TMTK back to number one.

00:41:57.786 --> 00:41:58.621
Really?

00:42:00.247 --> 00:42:03.667
So let's go eat something nice today.

00:42:03.751 --> 00:42:05.002
My treat!

00:42:05.502 --> 00:42:06.503
You're buying?

00:42:06.587 --> 00:42:08.255
It's on me today!

00:42:08.756 --> 00:42:10.758
PLANC
THE MAN TO KNOW

00:42:10.841 --> 00:42:13.719
Stop looking. Don't you get tired of it?

00:42:13.802 --> 00:42:17.765
Back when Mr. Cho got me and Yun Song
office spaces in the same building,

00:42:17.848 --> 00:42:21.560
he put me in the semi-basement
and her on the top floor. Did I tell you?

00:42:21.644 --> 00:42:22.978
A hundred times.

00:42:23.062 --> 00:42:26.523
I've been dreaming of this moment
since then.

00:42:26.607 --> 00:42:28.067
So stop being such a buzzkill.

00:42:28.651 --> 00:42:30.361
Fine. Enjoy it.

00:42:31.403 --> 00:42:32.905
But I feel bad for Ms. Seo.

00:42:34.782 --> 00:42:36.116
Do you think she's upset?

00:42:40.412 --> 00:42:41.497
I'm sure she is.

00:42:42.665 --> 00:42:45.501
God, it's freezing.
Why did we come all the way out here?

00:42:45.584 --> 00:42:47.086
How am I supposed to get home?

00:42:47.169 --> 00:42:49.338
You never get out of your neighborhood.

00:42:49.421 --> 00:42:50.923
They have amazing food here.

00:42:51.006 --> 00:42:52.883
What is this place? It's freezing.

00:42:53.592 --> 00:42:56.178
You can have whatever you want today!

00:42:57.846 --> 00:42:59.014
Isn't that Park?

00:43:02.059 --> 00:43:03.644
Damn it, let's go somewhere else.

00:43:03.727 --> 00:43:05.771
Ms. Yun. Hello.

00:43:07.773 --> 00:43:09.733
-Hello.
-Hi.

00:43:09.817 --> 00:43:11.151
Hello.

00:43:11.235 --> 00:43:15.072
Hwany's studio is around here, right?
Is this a celebration?

00:43:15.155 --> 00:43:18.075
We just had a meeting. What about you?

00:43:19.118 --> 00:43:21.412
We just came here to clear our heads.

00:43:23.455 --> 00:43:25.374
-How are you doing?
-Not well.

00:43:25.457 --> 00:43:27.126
-Cool.
-Damn it.

00:43:27.209 --> 00:43:30.003
-I said let's go.
-Right. We'll be going now.

00:43:30.087 --> 00:43:31.296
Annoying prick.

00:43:31.380 --> 00:43:33.507
Hell, we should have left before they did.

00:43:34.925 --> 00:43:36.093
Ms. Yun!

00:43:51.859 --> 00:43:53.569
I'm sorry I'm late.

00:43:53.652 --> 00:43:54.903
We're going somewhere else.

00:43:54.987 --> 00:43:56.989
-What? Where?
-Let's go.

00:43:57.072 --> 00:43:58.615
Wait!

00:44:01.952 --> 00:44:02.870
Wait a second.

00:44:12.045 --> 00:44:14.256
-Let me--
-No, I insist.

00:44:17.718 --> 00:44:18.844
Have some of this.

00:44:19.386 --> 00:44:21.472
-Thank you.
-No problem.

00:44:21.555 --> 00:44:24.183
What the heck is wrong with him?

00:44:26.059 --> 00:44:28.395
Hey, we'll be leaving soon. Keep it on.

00:44:28.479 --> 00:44:29.730
Man, such an eyesore.

00:44:29.813 --> 00:44:31.523
Oh, we're leaving soon?

00:44:32.649 --> 00:44:34.234
I'll just use the bathroom, then.

00:44:34.318 --> 00:44:35.319
Sure.

00:44:39.156 --> 00:44:40.741
Excuse me.

00:44:40.824 --> 00:44:43.827
Can you not ruin the mood?
You're making her walk on eggshells!

00:44:43.911 --> 00:44:46.789
Stop picking a fight.
I'll just take So-yeong and leave.

00:44:46.872 --> 00:44:49.917
Hey, that's just low. You can't do that.

00:44:50.000 --> 00:44:52.127
Why can't I do that?

00:44:52.211 --> 00:44:55.130
What will you offer to make us stay?
You going on hiatus?

00:44:55.923 --> 00:44:57.841
-Hiatus?
-Yeah!

00:45:00.093 --> 00:45:01.637
Sure. Yeah, I would--

00:45:03.931 --> 00:45:05.390
-Hey.
-What?

00:45:05.474 --> 00:45:09.812
Don't be so difficult.
We're negotiating as authors here.

00:45:10.479 --> 00:45:11.313
Ms. Yun.

00:45:11.814 --> 00:45:14.191
I'll do whatever you want.
Just don't take So-yeong.

00:45:14.817 --> 00:45:16.735
-Come on.
-Did you hear that?

00:45:17.945 --> 00:45:19.112
Please stop.

00:45:19.196 --> 00:45:21.740
Stop what?
You said we should do whatever it takes.

00:45:24.076 --> 00:45:25.327
So when are we leaving?

00:45:25.410 --> 00:45:26.954
What? We're not.

00:45:27.788 --> 00:45:28.789
What?

00:45:28.872 --> 00:45:30.958
The food here is good. You should eat up.

00:45:31.041 --> 00:45:33.669
-It's hot in here. Take off your coat.
-You should.

00:45:34.169 --> 00:45:35.462
Raise our glasses?

00:45:35.546 --> 00:45:37.089
-Yes!
-All right.

00:45:38.298 --> 00:45:39.132
Good stuff.

00:45:39.216 --> 00:45:41.260
-Cheers!
-Cheers!

00:45:41.760 --> 00:45:43.220
Goodness.

00:45:50.143 --> 00:45:52.855
There. Let's drink hard.

00:45:53.355 --> 00:45:55.440
Yeah, drink away.

00:45:55.524 --> 00:45:56.650
-Let's go!
-Let's go!

00:46:01.363 --> 00:46:03.115
Drink milk in the morning…

00:46:03.198 --> 00:46:04.116
Milk!

00:46:04.616 --> 00:46:05.450
She drinks milk.

00:46:06.827 --> 00:46:07.661
Oh, really?

00:46:08.620 --> 00:46:10.539
To like someone…

00:46:10.622 --> 00:46:14.042
Forward, into the heart of the enemy!

00:46:14.126 --> 00:46:15.377
It's here.

00:46:18.130 --> 00:46:20.299
…means coming up with excuses…

00:46:23.677 --> 00:46:24.678
Yes?

00:46:25.262 --> 00:46:28.599
Would you like to borrow this?
You can take your time returning it.

00:46:28.682 --> 00:46:30.934
-Oh, if you don't mind…
-Okay.

00:46:31.018 --> 00:46:33.520
…to spend more time together.

00:46:33.604 --> 00:46:37.190
So, So-yeong, this Christmas…

00:46:38.650 --> 00:46:40.027
Chris…

00:46:43.947 --> 00:46:45.240
Do you have plans for Christmas?

00:46:45.824 --> 00:46:49.036
Well, I guess I'll be watching anime
and movies at home.

00:46:49.119 --> 00:46:50.203
In that case--

00:46:50.287 --> 00:46:51.705
Sheesh, nowadays,

00:46:51.788 --> 00:46:54.958
the younger ones
are living duller lives than us.

00:46:55.042 --> 00:46:57.628
And your life is such a barrel of laughs?

00:46:57.711 --> 00:46:59.296
Have you got plans for Christmas?

00:46:59.379 --> 00:47:02.090
Hey, didn't I say last time
that I have a boyfriend?

00:47:02.174 --> 00:47:03.842
I told you.

00:47:03.926 --> 00:47:05.594
Right. So you said.

00:47:05.677 --> 00:47:07.346
You don't believe me, do you?

00:47:07.429 --> 00:47:09.848
Seo here even talked to my boyfriend
on the phone.

00:47:09.932 --> 00:47:11.725
-Right?
-Yes.

00:47:12.643 --> 00:47:13.477
Wait, really?

00:47:14.186 --> 00:47:15.020
Yes.

00:47:15.562 --> 00:47:17.314
He seemed to really like her.

00:47:18.982 --> 00:47:22.736
How do you find the time to meet him?
You're always working.

00:47:22.819 --> 00:47:23.654
Huh?

00:47:24.738 --> 00:47:25.822
You know, I just

00:47:26.323 --> 00:47:29.159
make do with what little time I can spare.

00:47:29.660 --> 00:47:33.455
Anyway, so am I the only one here
dating someone?

00:47:34.081 --> 00:47:37.501
What's wrong with all of you?
You're in your prime.

00:47:37.584 --> 00:47:39.169
Whatever.

00:47:39.836 --> 00:47:41.713
I'm jealous. So jealous.

00:47:42.547 --> 00:47:44.967
I think I'll just have more snacks.

00:47:48.428 --> 00:47:50.764
Damn it. It slipped my mind.

00:47:52.057 --> 00:47:53.558
We're out of snacks.

00:47:55.727 --> 00:47:57.729
We're also out of booze.

00:47:58.480 --> 00:48:00.148
Go get some more liquor.

00:48:20.252 --> 00:48:22.087
I…

00:48:24.756 --> 00:48:26.591
I'm sorry I lied to you.

00:48:28.385 --> 00:48:29.720
Lied to me about what?

00:48:31.346 --> 00:48:32.180
Well…

00:48:33.098 --> 00:48:36.351
You know,
how I told you that I had a boyfriend.

00:48:39.938 --> 00:48:42.941
I didn't mean to lie to you,

00:48:43.025 --> 00:48:47.362
but I'd never been in that situation
before, so I was panicking a little.

00:48:51.533 --> 00:48:52.451
I'm sorry too.

00:48:54.703 --> 00:48:55.537
What?

00:48:56.955 --> 00:49:00.417
I should've known bringing up my feelings
like that would make you uncomfortable,

00:49:01.376 --> 00:49:02.711
but I only thought of myself.

00:49:09.384 --> 00:49:11.470
Thank you for saying that.

00:49:12.637 --> 00:49:15.807
To be honest, recently,
it has been bothering me a bit.

00:49:16.475 --> 00:49:17.309
I kept

00:49:18.018 --> 00:49:21.730
thinking about how you said you were upset
before we left for Busan.

00:49:24.274 --> 00:49:25.609
I'm not upset anymore.

00:49:29.404 --> 00:49:30.280
Really?

00:49:32.657 --> 00:49:33.825
That's good.

00:49:39.748 --> 00:49:40.916
Ms. Seo.

00:49:42.959 --> 00:49:43.794
Yes?

00:49:46.213 --> 00:49:47.047
Now…

00:49:49.633 --> 00:49:52.135
is it official
that you don't have a boyfriend?

00:49:58.100 --> 00:49:59.935
Can I act like I'm also in the know?

00:50:03.313 --> 00:50:04.815
Yes, I guess so.

00:50:10.278 --> 00:50:11.196
From now on…

00:50:18.870 --> 00:50:20.622
can I do as I please?

00:53:41.364 --> 00:53:46.369
Subtitle translation by: Daham Yoon